snippet.title: [FNF] Rainbow Dash Tylenol
snippet.description:
Download mod: https://gamebanana.com/mods/370972
(MIDI, FLA, SF2, and chromatic scale are also available)

Original: Kitsune^2's Rainbow Tylenol

Note: This mod is an update from my older Rainbow Dash mod, the one that wears socks and self-aware dialogues: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fiLV5cvbns8

Android port by CatTino FNF: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8fli7EGCXdg
